org.gcn.plinguacore.util.psystem.factory

Class AbstractPsystemFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gcn.plinguacore.util.psystem.factory.AbstractPsystemFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPsystemFactory
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractCellLikePsystemFactory, SpikingPsystemFactory, TissueLikePsystemFactory

    public abstract class AbstractPsystemFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements IPsystemFactory
    This class is intended to be extended by a P-system factory for each supported model. Each factory should be able to create its own CheckRule instances (which makes sure the p-system complies with the model restrictions) and its own CreateSimulator, which should be able to create simulators for that model All AbstractPsystemFactory subclasses should follow the Singleton pattern.
